title: Like Sunday, Like Rain. Official Movie Trailer #1 [HD] (2015)
description:
In theaters: March 13th, 2015

Description:

Surrounded by wealth and living with abundant resources in Manhattan, 12-year-old cello prodigy Reggie lives a solitary life, lacking only frequently absent parents and friends. Estranged from family, having slacker boyfriend troubles, and fired from her waitressing job, sometimes musician 23-year-old Eleanor needs a new place to live and a new job. Fate winds her lovely fingers around these two lives to unexpectedly place the inexperienced Eleanor as the new au pair for a skeptical Reggie, and the music in their hearts and souls intertwines to create this beautiful story about discovery and acceptance.

Director: Frank Whaley

Writers: Frank Whaley

Actors: Leighton Meester, Billie Joe Armstrong, Debra Messing, Julian Shatkin

Genre: Drama

Run Time: 1 hour 45 minutes
